Isolating work in branches, changing context, and integrating changes

âž¡ git branch -> list your branches. a * will appear next to the currently active branch
âž¡ git branch [branch-name] -> create a new branch at the current commit
âž¡ git checkout -> switch to another branch and check it out in your working directory
