âœ… Ignoring Files

âž¡ $ cat .gitignore
/logs/*
!logs/.gitkeep
/tmp
*.swp

Verify the .gitignore file exists in your project and ignore certain types of files, such as all files in the logs directory (excluding the .gitkeep file),
 the whole tmp directory and all files *.swp. File ignoring will work for the directory (and children's directories) where the .gitignore file is placed.